channel.description:

Webclient: http://vyrescape.net/webclient.html
Vyre
Hey! Are you looking for a server but just can't seem to find one? Well you can stop looking now! This server has it all! Great economy, community, and also the best staff! Vyrescape features over 20+ players and also includes hours of fun! Join us now! You will not be disappointed!
Features
*Stable economy
*Most skills working
*Lots of training spots
*Lots of shops
*Vote shop with rewards
*Money pouch
*Skins
*Sheathing
*Ingame playtime
*Playtime rewards
*Crystal chest
*Dicing
*Working slayer
*Working dung
*Medium Exp
*All specials
*Lots of PVP areas
*Lots of PVM areas
*Corporeal beast
*King black dragon
*Queen black dragon
*Fight caves
*Kalphite queen
*All godwars bosses
*Donator zone and shops
